Temporary Female Administrator
BAC Middle East
MotorCity, UAE
Posted on: 4 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
AED 6000 Per Month
On behalf of our client a leading international diversified business company that is based at Motorcity Dubai we are looking to recruit a Temporary Female Administrator. You will cover an employees leave from June 1st to July 13th assisting with admin within the company. Please note this role will not become a permanent one
REQUIREMENTS
The successful candidate must be a resident of the UAE, be sponsored by your Husband and Father and be able to commence work on 01 June and work up until the 13 July. No transportation is provided therefore you must be able to arrange your own.
Fluency in English and UAE admin experience is essential.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
BAC Middle East - the longest established professional recruitment consultancy in the UAE. Established in 1979, we have been at the forefront of the region's recruitment industry for 30 years and were the first firm of our type in the world to achieve ISO9001 certification: a reflection of our constant emphasis on quality and customer satisfaction.
With our well-developed infrastructure and staff strength, we are able to assist you with recruitment needs ranging from junior professionals through to middle and senior management, whatever your industry sector.
BAC's proven regional experience and resources can help ensure that you recruit the best available candidates and enjoy the many advantages of a managed recruitment process.
